## ðŸ’» Technologies & Languages

### Primary Focus Areas

| Technology | Learning Focus | Defensive Application |
|------------|----------------|----------------------|
| **Python** | Security automation, tool development | Building security scanners, analysis tools |
| **JavaScript** | Web security, client-side attacks | Secure web development, XSS prevention |
| **C/C++** | Memory safety, low-level exploitation | Understanding buffer overflows, secure coding |
| **SQL** | Database security, injection techniques | Writing secure queries, input validation |
| **Bash/PowerShell** | System automation, scripting | Security automation, log analysis |
| **Assembly** | Reverse engineering, malware analysis | Understanding compiled code, debugging |
| **Java** | Android security, deserialization | Mobile app security, secure Java practices |

