## ðŸ” Final Thoughts

> *"Security is not a product, but a process."* - Bruce Schneier

Every vulnerability I study, every exploit I understand, every defense I implement - all of it makes me a better security practitioner. This isn't about breaking things; it's about understanding them so completely that I can protect them.

The journey from curious beginner to competent security professional is long, but rewarding. This repository is my proof of work.

**Stay curious. Stay ethical. Keep learning.**

